angedEventHandlerExample#1](~/add/codesnippet/cpp/t-system.componentmodel._106_1.cpp)]\"\n  syntax:\n    content: >-\n      [System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComVisible(true)]\n\n      public delegate void ComponentChangedEventHandler(object sender, ComponentChangedEventArgs e);\n  inheritance:\n  - System.Delegate\n  platform:\n  - net462\nreferences:\n- uid: System.Delegate\n  isExternal: false\n  name: System.Delegate\n"}